description: Uva Province - Appointed Hon. D. A. Chamara Sampath Dassanayake, Chief Minister as the Minister of Finance and Planning, etc, Hon. R. M. Kunarasiri Rathnayake as the Minister of Health & Indigenous Medicine, etc, Hon. A. S. thondaman Muththuvinayagam as the Minister of Road Development, etc, and Hon. B. S. Sumeda De Silva as the Minister of Sports & youth Affairs, etc, with effect from 22.10.2015
